        {
          "reviewTitle": "Decent foundation that will probably arrive damaged.",
          "reviewText": "It is a nice product, but came damaged. The foundation came cracked and stuck to the lid, and when the lid was removed, the stick snapped right off and then split into different pieces and made a mess. Consistency is a little weird too - a shard of foundation fell out of it (because it was a mess when it opened) and didn't realize it had gotten on my jeans. I looked down and a whole clump had come out and smeared itself everywhere, but there was still a chunk there. After warming up a bit, it had the consistency of like....playdoh. A little strange for foundation. I have a replacement coming because I reported it damaged on here, but the fact that it originally came this way tells me that the way it is packaged or created has a flaw, because makeup should never arrive in that condition, not if it is a high quality item made well and with care. So while the color seems fine and it works as a foundation stick should......it really has no business being that beat up on arrival - having to get replacements sent days later and send back the item to not get charged again all because they can't ship well doesn't make it a fun purchase.",
